<!DOCYTPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional //EN"
  "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %> - 弹幕墙</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='http://cdn.bootcss.com/twitter-bootstrap/3.0.2/css/bootstrap.min.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/base.css' />
    <!-- HTML5 shim, for IE6-8 support of HTML5 elements -->
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
      <script src="../assets/js/html5shiv.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
  </head>
  
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <ul class="nav nav-pills pull-right">
          <li class="active"><a href="#">主页</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">弹幕页面</a></li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="text-muted">弹幕墙</h3>
      </div>
      <form class="form-horizontal" role="form" action="/" method="post">
        &nbsp;
        <legend>发送弹幕</legend>
        <p>这里是弹幕发送页面，输入想发送的句子并选择好颜色，点击发送即可。</p>
        <p>有问题请联系brickgao#gmail.com</p>
        &nbsp;
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="sentence" class="col-sm-2 control-label">说点神马</label>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="sentence" placeholder="说点神马">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="color" class="col-sm-2 control-label">颜色</label>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <select id="color" class="form-control">
              <option value="">红</option>
              <option value="">橙</option>
              <option value="">黄</option>
              <option value="">绿</option>
              <option value="">青</option>
              <option value="">蓝</option>
              <option value="">紫</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="size" class="col-sm-2 control-label">大小</label>
          <div class="col-sm-10">
            <select id="size" class="form-control">
              <option value="">小</option>
              <option value="">普通</option>
              <option value="">大</option>
              <option value="">特大</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <div class="col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-10">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">发送</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; Brickgao 2013</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>

  <script src="http://libs.baidu.com/jquery/2.0.0/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="http://cdn.bootcss.com/twitter-bootstrap/3.0.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</html>
  
